{"tid":2187631,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今日係宣佈撤回一週年","createTime":"2020-09-03T17:55:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T20:02:36.000Z","uid":206117,"like":32,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ebfc13401714a519bf62050abc835760038a3941","tid":2187631,"uid":206117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T17:55:19.000Z","msg":"唔係有fb memories應該都唔會記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家記得嘅日子有好多<br />\n<br />\n6.9 100萬<br />\n6.12 圍堵<br />\n6.16 200萬<br />\n7.1 攻佔<br />\n7.21 唔見人<br />\n8.5 三罷<br />\n8.31 打死人<br />\n10.1 槍殺人<br />\n10.4 開花<br />\n11.11 黎明<br />\n不能盡錄<br />\n<br />\n但應該冇乜人記得9月4柒婆放個死人樣出嚟宣佈撤回, 證明當日佢哩個動作真係戇鳩到不值一提<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我記得當日好多手足放哩張相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9YSn2S4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9YSn2S4.jpg&h=b1387546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多謝大家冇收貨, 繼續撐到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b6f5b006938644c96a459eb7d938944ec596c7","tid":2187631,"uid":305602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T17:55:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab719f8fe15e80c5c022777334e6b101abbb973e","tid":2187631,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T17:59:44.000Z","msg":"如果嗰陣宣佈收手的話會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n起馬少左6千人被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b218b37ffe5c0a17e2f2c939929b1656299208b8","tid":2187631,"uid":95519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T18:07:59.000Z","msg":"印象中好似仲係垃會擾讓左陣先正式撤左？"},{"pid":"74ae44e8928365a9d5890d08495828d211f5be2f","tid":2187631,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b218b37ffe5c0a17e2f2c939929b1656299208b8","tid":2187631,"uid":95519,"like